image.altText: Drone images taken of native bush land showing dead patches with a few green trees.

props.synopsis: Only a small fraction of eucalyptus woodland remains alive in this region of Western Australia and the habitat loss is threatening wildlife and plant survival.

title.children: Hot, dry conditions kill masses of native vegetation in WA's Wheatbelt

image.altText: A close up shot of police tape with cars parked on a street and trees blurred in the background

props.synopsis: A man is been charged over an alleged hit and run in Perth's east that left a police officer with critical injuries.

image.altText: An older woman with short white hair sits on a chair in a clothing store. Her expression is neutral.

image.altText: Phillip Mehrtens sitting in a chair after being freed. He has long hair and a beard.
